

OpenToolbox is a symbolic control system designed to give composers complete control over almost all aspects of the musical score from inside the SuperCollider programming language. For this it uses GNU Lilypond as the music score render, also funcioning as a all purpose wrapper for Lilypond. 


---

SuperCollider dependencies (quarks): Tendency

System dependencies: Lilypond
              
---

Edit the ./setup.sc file to adapt everything to your system if necessary

